org.gbif.registry.persistence.mapper

Interface NodeMapper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseNetworkEntityMapper<org.gbif.api.model.registry.Node>, CommentableMapper, ContactableMapper, EndpointableMapper, IdentifiableMapper, MachineTaggableMapper, NetworkEntityMapper<org.gbif.api.model.registry.Node>, TaggableMapper

    public interface NodeMapper
extends BaseNetworkEntityMapper<org.gbif.api.model.registry.Node>
    For simplicity we keep ContactableMapper part of the BaseNetworkEntityMapper, but this NodeMapper does not implement those mapper methods but will throw exceptions instead ! For a Node all contacts are managed in the GBIF Filemaker IMS which we only access for reads and cannot manipulate though our Java API.
